Libwrite is a C library for generating files in Microsoft Write format.

The libwrite core was written in 1992 by Martin Guy <martinwguy@gmail.com>
and Windows build system and bindings for C and Visual Basic were written and
published as WriteKit by Claudio DeAngelis <c.deangelis@datart.it> in 1993.

The code here is the libwrite core, callable from C.

Documentation is in libwrite.md

Build and install

	make
	sudo make install
